\is1 Introduction
\ip This \bk First letter of Yohan (John)\bk* had two purposes: 1. encouraging the readers about God and his son Yeshua (Jesus) the messiah, and 2. warning them that it's important to not follow false or incorrect teachings that can destroy their unity with the messiah. These false teachers stated that Yeshua didn't become a person like us. They also taught that salvation doesn't include godly living and the love of others.
\ip So in refuting those false doctrines, Yohan carefully explained that Yeshua the messiah came to this world as a real person, and he also explained that all who believe in Yeshua and love God, must also demonstrate their love to each other.
\iot Main components of Yohan's letter
\io1 Introduction \ior 1:1-4\ior*
\io1 The darkness and the light \ior 1:5вҖ“2:29\ior*
\io1 The children of God and the children of Satan \ior 3:1-24\ior*
\io1 The truth and the lies \ior 4:1-6\ior*
\io1 About love \ior 4:7-21\ior*
\io1 Faith in Yeshua the messiah \ior 5:1-21\ior*
\rem This is still a very early look into the unfinished text of the Open English Translation of the Bible. Please double-check the text in advance before using in public.
\ie
\c 1
\s1 The message that is life
\rem /s1 Introduction; The Word of Life
\p
\v 1-3 We are reporting to you and testifying about what existed from the beginningВҰ151768:\x + \xo 1:1: \xt Yhn 1:1.\x* \bdit Yeshua the messiah and son of God\bdit*. We heard him, we saw him with our own eyesВҰ151774, and we touchedВҰ151782 him with our own handsВҰ151780. Concerning the messageВҰ151785 of life, we can also report and testify to you that that life was revealed\x + \xo 1:2: \xt Yhn 1:14.\x*вҖ”\add he is\add* the eternal life that was with the father and was revealed to us. We report what we've seen and what we've heard so that you all also can have fellowship with us, and our fellowship is with the father and with his son.
\v 4 We're writingВҰ151849 all this so that ourВҰ151855 joyВҰ151854 may be extended to you also.
\s1 We're all sinners
\rem /s1 God Is Light; Living in the Light; Fellowship, obedience, and forgiveness; Walking in the light
\p
\v 5 This is the messageВҰ151869 thatВҰ151870 we heardВҰ151871 from him and whichВҰ151870 we are declaringВҰ151875 to you all: \nd GodВҰ151880\nd* is lightВҰ151881 and there is no darknessВҰ151884 in himвҖ”none at all.
\v 6 If we sayВҰ151894 that we and himВҰ151899 are relating well together and yet we're walkingВҰ151904 in the darknessВҰ151903, then we're lyingВҰ151905 and not living the truthВҰ151911.
\v 7 ButВҰ151928 if we're walkingВҰ151917 in the light, just like he walks in the light, then we'll get along well with each other, and hisВҰ151935 son \nd Yeshua'sВҰ151931\nd* bloodВҰ151930 is removing the consequences of all our sins.
\p
\v 8 If we sayВҰ151942 that we don'tВҰ151945 have any sinВҰ151944, then we're \add just\add* fooling ourselvesВҰ151947 and haven't embraced the truthВҰ151952.
\v 9 \add ButВҰ151966\add* if we admit our sins, Yeshua is trustworthy and totally sinless, and he will forgiveВҰ151969 us for our sins and remove all of our guilt and consequences.
\v 10 If we sayВҰ151982 that we haven't sinnedВҰ151985, then we're makingВҰ151987 a liar out of Yeshua and we haven't internalised hisВҰ151992 messageВҰ151991.
\c 2
\s1 The messiah is our advocate
\rem /s1 Christ Our Advocate; Christ Our Helper
\p
\v 1 I am writingВҰ152000 to you all, myВҰ151998 treasured new believers, so that you might avoid sinning. If anyoneВҰ152007 should sin, we have an advocateВҰ152009 \add to help us relate to\add* the fatherВҰ152013: \nd Yeshua\nd* the sinless \nd messiahВҰ152015\nd*,
\v 2 and it's him who is the atonementВҰ152019 for our sinsвҖ”not just our sins, butВҰ152017 also the sins of the entireВҰ152036 worldВҰ152038.
\p
\v 3 We will know if we \add really\add* know Yeshua if we obey hisВҰ152050 teachings.
\v 4 If someone says that they know Yeshua butВҰ152058 don'tВҰ152062 do what he taught, that person is a liar and hasn't internalised the truthВҰ152070.
\v 5 However the person who obeys Yeshua's teaching demonstrates that God's loveВҰ152086 has trulyВҰ152082 been planted in them. We know that we are \add alive\add* in Yeshua if
\v 6 we claim to live in himВҰ152100 and then live our lives like he lived.
\s1 Love not hate to be in the light
\rem /s1 A New Commandment; The New Command
\p
\v 7 \x + \xo 2:7: \xt Yhn 13:34.\x*Dear friends, I'm not writingВҰ152115 a new rule for you all, but \add reminding you\add* of an old rule that you had from the beginningВҰ152123. This old rule is the messageВҰ152130 that you all heardВҰ152132.
\v 8 Then again I \em am\em* writingВҰ152138 a new rule to youвҖ”a rule whichВҰ152140 is true in Yeshua and in you all, becauseВҰ152151 the darknessВҰ152154 is already disappearing and the true lightВҰ152158 is already shiningВҰ152163.
\p
\v 9 Anyone who says they're in the lightВҰ152168 butВҰ152170 hates a fellow believer,\f + \fr 2:9 \ft Literally вҖҳour brothersвҖҷ. In this letter that term could refer to вҖҳsiblingsвҖҷ, вҖҳfellow believersвҖҷ, or вҖҳfellow citizensвҖҷ (or Yohan could be alternating between two or three of them in his mind as he wrote). After considering all the uses of the term in chapters 2вҖ“5, we have taken вҖҳfellow believersвҖҷ as being more likely, i.e., the context would often seem to be focussing on believers (even though most of us would want to apply 3:16вҖ“17 to also include вҖҳfellow citizensвҖҷ).\f* is still in the darknessВҰ152180.
\v 10 It's the person that loves their fellow believers who is living in the lightВҰ152191 andВҰ152193 doesn't offendВҰ152194 anyone.
\v 11 ButВҰ152211 the person who hates a fellow believer is living and walkingВҰ152215 in the darkness and doesn't know whereВҰ152219 they're goingВҰ152220 becauseВҰ152221 they're blindedВҰ152224.
\s1 Don't love the things of this world
\p
\v 12 I'm writingВҰ152229 to you new believers because your sinsВҰ152237 have been forgivenВҰ152233 because of Yeshua authority.
\v 13 I'm writing to you fathersВҰ152244 because you have knownВҰ152246 the messiah from the beginningВҰ152249.\x + \xo 2:13: \xt Lk 2:25-35.\x*
\v 14 I wrote to you new believers because you have know the fatherВҰ152266. I wrote to you fathersВҰ152269 because you have known the messiah from the beginningВҰ152275.\x + \xo 2:13: \xt Lk 2:25-35.\x* I wrote to you youngВҰ152278 menВҰ152278 because you are strongВҰ152280 and God's messageВҰ152284 lives in you and you have overcomeВҰ152291 the evil one.
\rem /s1 Do Not Love the World
\p
\v 15 Don't be loving the world nor the things in the world. The father'sВҰ152314 love does not live in anyoneВҰ152304 who loves the world
\v 16 because everything that's in the world, bodily desires and lusts and arrogantВҰ152334 livingВҰ152336, is not from the fatherВҰ152341 butВҰ152327 from the world.
\v 17 And the worldВҰ152349 will come to an end along with the desire for itВҰ152354, butВҰ152356 the person obeying God's desires will continue to live.
\s1 Beware of вҖҳnewвҖҷ teaching
\rem /s1 The danger of false teaching; Warning against Antichrists; The Enemy of Christ
\p
\v 18 New believers, it's now the last times and what youВҰ152375 heardВҰ152375 about the false messiah comingВҰ152379 is now happening. Many false messiahs have already been around and that confirms that it's now the last times.
\v 19 They cameВҰ152394 from ourВҰ152398 group, but they were never truly part of us becauseВҰ152401 if they were, they would have stayed with us. But they leftВҰ152394 us so it would be revealedВҰ152412 that they're not part of us.
\p
\v 20 But you all have received the spirit\f + \fr 2:20 \ft anointing: It's not really clear here what Yohan is referring to that they have received: God's favour? a skill or ability? a blessing? the Holy Spirit? But v27 below seems to be talking about God's holy spirit.\f* from the chosen messiah\f + \fr 2:20 \ft holy (one): Yohan seems to be referring to Yeshua here.\f* andВҰ152419 you all know all about it.\f + \fr 2:20 \ft You all know all: also unclear what Yohan means.\f*
\v 21 I didn'tВҰ152430 write to you all because you don'tВҰ152430 know the truth, butВҰ152442 because you have known the truth and any falsehoodВҰ152445 is not part of it.
\p
\v 22 \nd AnyoneВҰ152465\nd* who teaches that \nd Yeshua\nd* is not the messiah is a liar. And \nd anyoneВҰ152465\nd* who disowns the fatherВҰ152474 andВҰ152475 the son is a false messiah.
\v 23 Anyone who disownsВҰ152480 the son, doesn't know the father eitherвҖ”only those who confessВҰ152488 the son know the father
\p
\v 24 What you all heard from the beginning, that's what you shouldВҰ152504 hold to. If the message that you heard from the beginning remains in you, then you also will remain in the son and in the fatherВҰ152524,
\v 25 andВҰ152526 in thatВҰ152531 case, what he promisedВҰ152533 us is to live forever.
\p
\v 26 I wroteВҰ152542 theseВҰ152540 things to you all concerningВҰ152544 those who would misleadВҰ152546 you.
\v 27 ButВҰ152548 for you, the spirit that you receivedВҰ152554 from Yeshua remains in you all and so you don'tВҰ152563 need anyoneВҰ152567 else to teach you because hisВҰ152575 spirit teaches you about everything. The spirit teaches truth and not lies, and since you were taughtВҰ152593 by the spirit thenВҰ152548 you are remaining in Yeshua.
\rem /s1 Children of God
\p
\v 28 SoВҰ152599 now you new believers, remainВҰ152602 in him so that when he is revealedВҰ152608, we can have boldnessВҰ152611 andВҰ152599 not be ashamedВҰ152614 of him when he comes \add back\add*.
\rem /s1 Children of God
\v 29 Because you know that he is sinless, you also know that anyone faithfully obeying hisВҰ152637 teaching has been \add re\add*born in him.
\c 3
\s1 Living as God's children
\rem /s1 How Christians live together; Living as Children of God
\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 3:1: \xt Yhn 1:12.\x*Consider the amazing live that the fatherВҰ152649 has givenВҰ152644 to us in orderВҰ152650 that we can be calledВҰ152653 God's childrenВҰ152651, and indeed we are.
\v 2 Dear friends we are God's childrenВҰ152670 now, butВҰ152673 it's not yet revealed what we will become. We know that when Yeshua is revealed, we will be similarВҰ152683 to him becauseВҰ152686 then we'll be seeingВҰ152687 him exactly as he is.
\v 3 Everyone who trusts their future to himВҰ152699 needs to purifyВҰ152700 themself just like he is pure.
\p
\v 4 EveryoneВҰ152706 who regularly sins is demonstrating lawlessness, and sin is lawlessness.
\v 5 \x + \xo 3:5: \xt Yhn 1:29.\x*You all know that Yeshua was revealedВҰ152727 in orderВҰ152728 to takeВҰ152732 away sinsВҰ152730, andВҰ152733 there's no sinВҰ152734 in himВҰ152736.
\v 6 EveryoneВҰ152741 who remainsВҰ152745 in him doesn't sinвҖ”everyoneВҰ152748 who keeps sinning has neitherВҰ152751 really seenВҰ152752 Yeshua nor knownВҰ152755 him.
\p
\v 7 So new believers, don't let anyoneВҰ152759 deceiveВҰ152762 you: the person faithfully obeying Yeshua's teaching will be declared not guilty just as he is not guilty.
\v 8 Anyone who regularly sins belongs to the devil, becauseВҰ152783 the devil has been sinningВҰ152788 from the beginningВҰ152785.
\p
\v 9 EveryoneВҰ152802 who's been \add re\add*born in God, doesn't regularly sin because God's seed \add of life\add* remainsВҰ152816 in them and thatВҰ152803 person isn'tВҰ152809 able to sin because they have been \add re\add*born in God.
\v 10 You can distinguish God's children and the devil'sВҰ152838 children like this: everyoneВҰ152840 who doesn't faithfully obey Yeshua's teaching or doesn't love their fellow believers, thatВҰ152841 person doesn't belong to God.
\s1 Demonstrate your love for each other
\rem /s1 Love One Another
\p
\v 11 \x + \xo 3:11: \xt Yhn 13:34.\x*Yes, this is the messageВҰ152863 that youВҰ152865 all heardВҰ152865 from the beginningВҰ152867: to be lovingВҰ152869 each otherвҖ”
\v 12 not living like CainВҰ152873 who belonged to the evil one andВҰ152883 went on to murder his brother.\x + \xo 3:12: \xt Gen 4:8.\x* And why did he kill him? BecauseВҰ152888 his own actions were evil, butВҰ152883 his brother \add Hevel/Abel\add* followed God's instructions.
\p
\v 13 And friends, don't be surprised if the worldВҰ152909 hates youВҰ152907.
\v 14 \x + \xo 3:14: \xt Yhn 5:24.\x*We know that we have transferred from death to life becauseВҰ152921 we are loving our fellowВҰ152924 believersВҰ152924. Anyone who doesn't love others is stuck in death.
\v 15 EveryoneВҰ152935 who hates another person is a murderer, andВҰ152944 youВҰ152945 all know thatВҰ152936 murderers don'tВҰ152949 have eternalВҰ152952 lifeВҰ152951 in them.
\v 16 We know about \add real\add* loveВҰ152961 becauseВҰ152962 we saw that Yeshua gave up hisВҰ152968 lifeВҰ152967 for us, and we should give up our livesВҰ152977 for our fellowВҰ152975 believersВҰ152975.
\v 17 ButВҰ152988 anyone who's enjoying being alive and notices that a fellow believer is in need yet shuts that other believer's needs out of their conscience, how can God's loveВҰ153004 be livingВҰ152985 in that person?
\v 18 So you new believers, don'tВҰ153012 just proclaim that you're lovingВҰ153013 people, butВҰ153019 actually demonstrate it in actions andВҰ153022 in fact.
\rem /s1 Courage before God
\v 19 That's how we'll know that the truthВҰ153032 really is in us.
\p At the same time, we need to tell ourselves
\v 20 that if we are feeling condemnedВҰ153047, \nd GodВҰ153056\nd* is greaterВҰ153052 than ourВҰ153048 feelings and he knows everything.
\v 21 Then dear friends, if we're not feeling condemnedВҰ153073, we have confidenceВҰ153077 in \nd GodВҰ153082\nd*
\v 22 and confidence that whateverВҰ153084 we are requestingВҰ153087 from him, we will receiveВҰ153089 it becauseВҰ153094 we are following hisВҰ153097 instructions and doing the things that pleaseВҰ153102 him.
\v 23 \x + \xo 3:23: \xt Yhn 13:34; 15:12,17.\x*And this is his command: We need to believeВҰ153114 in the authority of his son, Yeshua the \nd messiahВҰ153121\nd*, andВҰ153106 we should love each other as per the command that Yeshua gave to us.
\v 24 Anyone who follows hisВҰ153135 commandsВҰ153134 is living in him, and he is living in them and we have confirmation that he is living in us, because we have the \nd spiritВҰ153153\nd* that he gaveВҰ153156 to us.
\c 4
\s1 True and false spirits
\rem /s1 Test the Spirits; Testing the Spirits; Discerning False Prophets; The True Spirit and the False Spirit; Spirits of truth and error
\p
\v 1 Dear friends, don'tВҰ153161 trust everyВҰ153162 spiritВҰ153163, butВҰ153166 test them to determine whetherВҰ153170 or not it's from \nd GodВҰ153173\nd*, becauseВҰ153175 many falseВҰ153177 prophetsВҰ153177 go around the worldВҰ153181.
\v 2 You all can find out whether or not a spirit is from God: If the spirit confessesВҰ153199 that \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ153202\nd* has come as a person, then it's from God
\v 3 but if the spirit won'tВҰ153215 confessВҰ153216 \nd Yeshua\nd*, thenВҰ153229 it's not from \nd GodВҰ153226\nd* but rather it's the spirit of the false messiah, whom you've heardВҰ153237 is comingВҰ153240, andВҰ153229 is now alreadyВҰ153247 in the worldВҰ153245.
\p
\v 4 You new believers are in \nd GodВҰ153251\nd* and you have defeated the \add false prophets\add*, becauseВҰ153257 the one in you is more powerful than the one in the worldВҰ153267.
\v 5 They belong to the world hence theyВҰ153278 are speakingВҰ153278 from the world, andВҰ153279 the world is listening to them.
\v 6 However we belong to God, and anyone who knows God listens to us, butВҰ153313 anyone who doesn't belong to God can'tВҰ153296 accept what we're saying. That's how we can distinguish the spirit of truthВҰ153312 from deceptiveВҰ153317 spirits.
\s1 Loving God means loving others
\rem /s1 Love one another; God's Love and Ours; God Is Love; Loving One Another
\p
\v 7 Dear friends, we need to be loving each other, becauseВҰ153321 love is from God and everyoneВҰ153329 who \add truly\add* loves has been \add re\add*born into God and knows God.
\v 8 Those who don't love, don't love God becauseВҰ153350 God is love.
\v 9 God's loveВҰ153359 was revealedВҰ153357 to us when he sentВҰ153370 hisВҰ153367 only son to be born into the worldВҰ153375 so that we can liveВҰ153377 throughВҰ153379 him.
\v 10 So this is \add real\add* loveВҰ153385, not us loving God, butВҰ153396 God loving us andВҰ153402 sending hisВҰ153407 son to be the sacrifice to clear us of the sentence from ourВҰ153412 sinsВҰ153411.
\p
\v 11 Dear friends, if \nd GodВҰ153417\nd* loves us like that, weВҰ153421 oughtВҰ153422 to be lovingВҰ153424 each other.
\v 12 \x + \xo 4:12: \xt Yhn 1:18.\x*No one has ever seenВҰ153428 God, butВҰ153439 when weВҰ153432 are lovingВҰ153432 each other then God is living in us, andВҰ153439 hisВҰ153442 loveВҰ153441 is being perfectedВҰ153443 in us.
\p
\v 13 We can know that we are living in him and him in us becauseВҰ153460 he has givenВҰ153465 to us from hisВҰ153464 \nd spiritВҰ153463\nd*.
\v 14 And weВҰ153469 have seenВҰ153470 andВҰ153472 are testifyingВҰ153473 that the fatherВҰ153476 sentВҰ153477 the sonвҖ”the saviourВҰ153480 of the worldВҰ153482.
\v 15 Anyone who confessesВҰ153486 that \nd Yeshua\nd* is God's son, God lives in that person andВҰ153501 they live in God.
\v 16 We have knownВҰ153510 and experienced the love that God has in us.
\p God is love, and anyone who lives in love, lives in God, and God lives in them.
\v 17 This is how loveВҰ153547 will be perfectedВҰ153545 in us so that we can live with confidenceВҰ153553 about the \add coming\add* judgementВҰ153561 dayВҰ153558: we live like Yeshua in this worldВҰ153572.
\v 18 There's no fear in love, but rather perfect love drives away fear, becauseВҰ153588 our fear is that of being punishedВҰ153591 but the one fearingВҰ153595 has not been perfected in love.
\p
\v 19 We love others becauseВҰ153607 heВҰ153610 lovedВҰ153612 us firstВҰ153611.
\v 20 Anyone who says that they are loving God butВҰ153621 hates a fellow believer, that person is liar becauseВҰ153629 if someone can't love a fellow believer that they've seen, they can't love God who they've never seen.
