\p
\v 1 EveryoneВҰ153665 who believesВҰ153667 that \nd YeshuaВҰ153669\nd* is the \nd messiahВҰ153672\nd* has been \add re\add*born in \nd GodВҰ153675\nd*, and everyoneВҰ153678 who loves the father who gave birth to us, also loves the son that he gave birth to.
\v 2 We can know when we love God's childrenВҰ153696: wheneverВҰ153699 we love God and obey hisВҰ153706 commandsВҰ153705,
\v 3 becauseВҰ153710 the definition of loving \nd GodВҰ153715\nd*\x + \xo 5:3: \xt Yhn 14:15.\x* is obeying his commands and his commands are not a big strain on us
\v 4 becauseВҰ153728 everyoneВҰ153729 who's been \add re\add*born in \nd GodВҰ153734\nd* is overcomingВҰ153735 the world.
\v 5 SoВҰ153753 who can overcomeВҰ153756 the worldВҰ153758? Only the person who believesВҰ153762 that \nd Yeshua\nd* is God's son.
\s1 God's testimony about Yeshua
