\p
\v 6 \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ153782\nd* is the one who was born by water and blood and spiritвҖ”not by water only,\x + \xo 5:6: \xt Yhn 3:5-8.\x* butВҰ153798 by water and by blood
\v 7 because there are threeВҰ153812 that testifyВҰ153815:
\v 8 the \nd spiritВҰ153842\nd*, the waterВҰ153845, and the bloodВҰ153848, and these threeВҰ153851 come together into one.
\v 9 If we accept testimonies from people, then God's testimony is better, becauseВҰ153870 God's testimony is about hisВҰ153883 son.
\v 10 Any person that believes that \add Yeshua is\add* God's son has internalised God's testimony, but anyone who doesn't believe in God calls him a liar becauseВҰ153908 they have not believed the testimony of God himselfВҰ153897 about hisВҰ153922 son.
\v 11 And this is the testimonyВҰ153927: that \nd GodВҰ153934\nd* gave eternalВҰ153930 life to us\x + \xo 5:11: \xt Yhn 3:36.\x* andВҰ153923 this life is in hisВҰ153944 son.
\v 12 Anyone who has the son has life, but anyone who doesn't have the god's son, doesn't have \add eternal\add* life.
\s1 Living without ending
\rem /s1 Epilogue; Concluding Remarks; Conclusion; Final instructions and encouragement; Eternal Life
\p
\v 13 I wroteВҰ153965 theseВҰ153964 things to you so that you all could know that you have eternalВҰ153972 lifeВҰ153970, that is the ones believedВҰ153976 in the nameВҰ153980 and authority of God's son.
\v 14 And so we have confidenceВҰ154006 in God that if we requestВҰ154016 anythingВҰ154015 accordingВҰ154017 to hisВҰ154021 will, he hears us
\v 15 whateverВҰ154032 we're requestingВҰ154035, andВҰ154025 we know that we'll receive what we requestedВҰ154044.
\p
\v 16 If anyoneВҰ154049 sees a fellow believer committing a forgivable sin, then that person should ask God on their behalf and God will give life to that fellow believer. (ButВҰ154061 there is a sin that \add always\add* results in death and I'm not suggesting that we should ask in that case.)
\v 17 All disobedience is sin, butВҰ154087 thereВҰ154088 are sins that don'tВҰ154090 \add necessarily\add* lead to deathВҰ154092.
\p
\v 18 We know thatВҰ154096 everyoneВҰ154095 who's been \add re\add*born into God doesn't keep sinningВҰ154102, butВҰ154103 the \add messiah\add* who was born from God watches over them andВҰ154112 so the evilВҰ154114 one can'tВҰ154101 touchВҰ154116 them.
\p
\v 19 We know that weВҰ154123 belong to \nd GodВҰ154122\nd* andВҰ154124 that the wholeВҰ154127 word is under the control of the evilВҰ154130 one.
\p
\v 20 We know that God's son has come and helped our minds so that we could know the true one, and we are in the true one and \add also\add* in hisВҰ154162 son, \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ154165\nd*вҖ”the true God and eternalВҰ154175 lifeВҰ154174 \add itself\add*.
\p
\v 21 You new believers, don't honour idolsВҰ154182.
